abstract: Danny Wimmer Presents, which produces music festivals like Rock on the Range, is selling a stake in itself to the United Auburn Indian Community Development Corporation.

byline.original: By MICHAEL J. DE LA MERCED

headline.main: Native American Tribe Buys Stake in Rock Festival Producer Danny Wimmer
